## ▶️ How to Run

### 1️⃣ Clone the Repository
```
git clone https://github.com/Praneetha-as29/ML-MODEL-DETECTION.git
```

### 2️⃣ Open in Colab / Jupyter
Upload the notebooks or open directly in Google Colab  

### 3️⃣ Install Dependencies (if required)
```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 4️⃣ Run the Project
Execute all cells step-by-step  

